## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [nrp1-1/nrp2-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Double mutant displays early senescence at 21 days post germination. Increased rate of cell death. Decreased stress tolerance.
   - [nrp1-1/nrp2-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Dwarf phenotype, with smaller cotyledons and true leaves, and a significantly shorter primary root compared with the wild-type. Early senescence.
